      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LILLY DRAGON (8) hit the ground running from a squeeze draw and prominent early but run ended and faded to finish 7th at Capalaba in Grade 5 company. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can make amends. SWEET LADETTE (3) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when second beaten 4.5 lengths (19.84). Comes through a solid form race last start. Leading chance. ROLLING ROYALTY (6) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Capalaba over 366m behind Jimary Bob (20.24) in a P5. Has good early speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. LOST DRAGON (4) can fill a top-three spot.",
